  <brief_title>Efficacy of Sprayable PEG Barrier in Gynecologic Laparoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Polyethylene Glycol Adhesion Barrier Reduces Adhesions After Gynecologic Laparoscopy; a Prospective Randomized Controlled Pilot Study</official_title>
