  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt;18 years

          -  Undergoing gynecologic laparoscopy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Suspected malignancy

          -  Incomplete adhesiolysis during initial laparoscopy

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Lactating

          -  Stage IV endometriosis
      </textblock>
